messages.message:
Hey team, I've created a series of PFRs based on the discussion we had with ANZs architecture/IDP team last night around deployment metrics. Here is the list of requests:
• Access metrics at the validation rule level: https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-3390
• Enable performance notifications of deployed solutions: https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-3392
• Value metrics at org/workspace level: https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-3393
• Org level retention policy: https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-3394
• Expose/document Opensearch APIs to users: https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-3395
